      • getNegationMutationRatio

        public Double getNegationMutationRatio()
        If this ratio is set to anything greater 0, the Concept creation allows random negation mutations on the concepts. The original concept will still be added, however a concept containing a Complement of a part of it might be added as well
        Returns:
        negationMutationRatio

      • setNegationMutationRatio

        public void setNegationMutationRatio​(Double negationMutationRatio)
        If this ratio is set to anything greater 0, the Concept creation allows random negation mutations on the concepts. The original concept will still be added, however a concept containing a Complement of a part of it might be added as well
        Parameters:
        negationMutationRatio - negation mutation ratio

      • getMaxLateralDepth

        public Integer getMaxLateralDepth()
        Lateral Depth allows combinations using laterals rather than recursive. Allowing expressions like A and B and C if set to 2 f.e. However this might lead to a OOM as a lot of expressions are generated.
        Returns:
        maxLateralDepth

      • setMaxLateralDepth

        Parameters:
        maxLateralDepth - maximum lateral depth
